PROVENANCE
----------
This repository was extracted from skyphusion-labs/vivijure-cf at commit
59b3fb382521cab36cc0a746f77b174635133552 (2026-07-18), per vivijure-cf issue #85.

The pre-extraction history of this code remains in vivijure-cf; no history was
rewritten in either repository. vivijure-cf stays a clean, self-hostable Studio
with no requirement to operate a hosted service; this repository holds the
hosted-service machinery only.

The two repositories are coupled ONLY through the published Studio release
artifact (the versioned bundle contract: {tag, manifest_sha256} pinned by the
provisioner). There are no source-level imports across the boundary, and there
must never be.

A labor of love, given freely: use it, learn from it, self-host it, build your own
creative visions on it. Run it as a network service and the AGPL has you share your
changes back, so it stays a commons. It is NOT for sale, and NOT to be resold as a SaaS.
